{"tid":1466593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"失敗撚 分化撚 捉鬼撚 仲之有關心個香港既都入黎","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:41.000Z","uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4429ac80da77455a7161f31f8026b3b92f3bf463","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"首先咪撚再互屌 <br />\n第二 唔好因為一件事就話輸晒<br />\n<br />\n由69開始冇人擔保一直做緊既野係100%正確，今晚機場都一樣，就算係有錯，之後咪改，你真係諗住成個反送中一件事都唔做錯，好順利咁推翻個政府，黑警 林鄭錯完又錯咪一樣係到兜緊,日日開記招撚到啲藍絲覺得佢地做既野合情合理，我地一樣得，我地文宣人才一定勁過對家。<br />\n想話比大家知唔好咁易認輸，就算輸都要對家一齊攬抄就係咁簡單，大家諗下點樣拆掂今晚情況好過。<br />\n<br />\n好多手足等緊我地去救，爆眼女義士，荃灣被斬手足，爆門牙救人手足，40幾個被人告暴動前線兄弟 仲有好多好多都靠我地 唔好認輸"},{"pid":"f79e5ddafd3b6a9aa35f85269950f00f4a68979d","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:26.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"517605d6007238dac167b6f60bc13d35ac2d9372","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"cf1ce8085451e3dc45f2f71d9bb072fa507ca5e7","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"805"},{"pid":"a77ccaadddc0652af8a0c6c8d5d187fa0303b66e","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"50b5b41552ac104e3f555d62c19f0e68d7825447","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"7e28c116c02255102dab9fbd1849d5b82f710ece","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"805"},{"pid":"3e8da66fe2bdb2ca1c3bf24676aa920f9ab8c075","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"7b6529d690eeb21c43b044609c99e075f0fd1595","tid":1466593,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci